        <kanji>辱止念行弖</kanji>
        <transcription>katadikena si to omoposite</transcription>
      </sentence>
      <sentence n="8">
        <kanji>挂久毛畏岐</kanji>
        <transcription>kake ma ku mo kasikwo ki</transcription>
      </sentence>
      <sentence n="9">
        <kanji>聖天皇朝太政大臣止之弖</kanji>
        <transcription>piziri no sumyera ga mikadwo opo maturi goto no opo mapye tu kimi to site</transcription>
      </sentence>
      <sentence n="10">
        <kanji>仕奉止勅祁礼止</kanji>
        <transcription>sikape mature to nori tamapi kyeredo</transcription>
      </sentence>
      <sentence n="11">
        <kanji>数々辞備申多夫仁依弖</kanji>
        <transcription>siba siba ina bwi mawosi tabu ni yori te</transcription>
      </sentence>
      <sentence n="12">
        <kanji>受賜多婆受成尔志</kanji>
        <transcription>uke tamapari taba zu nari ni si</transcription>
      </sentence>
      <sentence n="13">
        <kanji>事毛悔止</kanji>
        <transcription>koto mo kuyasi to</transcription>
      </sentence>
      <sentence n="14">
        <kanji>念賀故仁今此藤原恵美朝臣能大保乎大師乃官仁仕奉止授賜夫</kanji>
        <transcription>omoposu ga yuwe ni ima ko no pudi para no wemi asomi no daipou wo daisi no tukasa ni tukape mature to saduke tama pu</transcription>
      </sentence>
      <sentence n="15">
        <kanji>天皇御命衆聞食宣</kanji>
        <transcription>sumyera ga opo mikoto wo moro moro kiki tamapeyo to noritamapu</transcription>
      </sentence>
